I"–<p>A little tip on Adobe Illustrator: A simple way to draw interesting patterns by AI: Pressing the <code class="highlighter-rouge">~</code> button on the keyboard, then choose any shapes you like, and then click left button of mouse, and draw any path you want the center point of the shape to follow, and then you can get cool patterns!</p>

